*capi4k-utils-20050718-r1 (03 Sep 2005)

  03 Sep 2005; Stefan Briesenick <sbriesen@gentoo.org> files/capi.blacklist,
  files/capi.conf, files/capi.confd, files/capi.hotplug, files/capi.initd,
